<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.10">
<l>māyavaṉ piṉvaḻi ceṉṟu vaḻiyiṭai māṟṟaṅkaḷ kēṭ</l>
<l>ṭāyarkaḷ cēriyi lumpuk kaṅkuttai māṟṟamu mellān</l>
<l>tāyavaḷ colliya collait taṇputu vaippaṭṭaṉ coṉṉa</l>
<l>tūyata miḻppattum vallār tūmaṇi vaṇṇaṉukkā ḷarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master [this] ten of pure Tamil</l>
<l rend="indent">composed by the scholar of cool Putuvai,</l>
<l>about the words that were spoken by [this] mother,</l>
<l rend="indent">going along the path following Māyavaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">asking questions on the path,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and,] having entered the herder village,</l>
<l rend="indent">all the words [she spoke] in that place,</l>
<l>they are devotees of the pure jewel hued [lord].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
